graph TD
    classDef layer fill:#f9f9f9,stroke:#ddd,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef core fill:#e1f5fe,stroke:#03a9f4,stroke-width:2px;

    User([开发者]) -->|"/super-dev 需求"| Host[宿主层<br>Claude Code / IDE 等]
    Host -->|触发集成规则| Adapter[接入适配层<br>rules / slash 映射]
    
    Adapter --> Engine{{核心编排引擎<br>WorkflowEngine}}:::core
    
    Engine -->|1. 策略拦截| Policy[策略治理]
    Engine -->|2. 背景挂载| Knowledge[领域知识库]
    Engine -->|3. 调度推演| Experts[专家系统协作]
    
    Experts -->|生成内容| Builders[文档与代码生成器]
    Builders -->|校验产物| Reviewers[红队与质量门禁]
    
    Reviewers -- 质量阻断 --> Engine
    Reviewers -- 通过发布 --> Deploy[部署与交付包]
    
    Deploy --> Output[(output/ 最终产物)]
